data.description: MASSIVE PRICE REDUCTION AS SELLERS ARE BUYING A HOME ELSEWHERE AND NEED TO SELL ASAP.  Are you looking for one of the best elementary schools (Big Ridge) in the Chattanooga area?  Want to be close to downtown? Want to be close to a lake community pier and the Hixson Greenway at an affordable price? How about a home with plenty of yard for the kids to play in, but with all the privacy a family could need?  Come check out 4714 Gann Store Road in desirable Hixson, TN.  Owners have cleared all trees towering over home as well as many in back to make for a bigger and safer yard.  They also added LTV flooring in the Master bedroom and did a LOT of fresh painting and added a new microwave oven.  There is extra storage to be found above garage and above laundry room.  The home is move in ready.  When you visit the home, be sure to take in all the granite, cabinets, open space and proximity to endless shopping and restaurants in Hixson.
